# Premium Design and Architecture Guidelines

## Role and Standard
- Act as an award-winning Awwwards designer and enforce absolute pixel-perfection for every single component before moving to the next.

## Wow-Factor Visual System
- Use glassmorphism effects with subtle background blurs and soft noise textures.
- Add dynamic hover states with glowing neon accents on deep dark backgrounds.
- Use liquid-like page transitions with Framer Motion and avoid hard cuts.
- Implement magnetic buttons that subtly follow the mouse pointer for a premium feel.

## Clean Architecture Rules
- Use a strict feature-based folder architecture to keep modules isolated and maintainable.
- Maintain absolute separation between UI components and business logic.
- Use a global theme provider to enforce spacing scale and golden-ratio typography consistently.

## Typography
- Prefer premium highly legible fonts like Plus Jakarta Sans or Inter with generous whitespace.
